Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.20,Nói chuyện - Selector,W,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.60,Nói chuyện - Selector,W,0,0,0,,Chỉ là cạnh tranh thôi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:00.62,Nói chuyện - Selector,W,0,0,0,,Bell này,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.45,Nói chuyện - Selector,W,0,0,0,,muốn giao ước trực tiếp không?
