Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:38.21,Nói chuyện - Selector,G,0,0,0,,Aiz?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:42.38,Nói chuyện - Selector,R,0,0,0,,Có vẻ như cô ấy cũng nóng ruột rồi.
